snippet.title: PicoMix by Nusan - Trailer
snippet.description:
PicoMix by NuSan is a compilation of works in multiple genres, like platform, puzzle, crafting, or base building for a total of about 20 fun games and experiments made using the Pico8 Fantasy Console
The game will be released on January 16 2025 on Steam, Itch.io and Nintendo Switch
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3276220/PicoMix_by_NuSan/
